title: Chinese Super League star Qin Sheng banned for SIX MONTHS for horrific stamping on Belgian star Axel Witsel
text:
EFL QIN AND BEAR IT Chinese Super League star Qin Sheng banned for SIX MONTHS for horrific stamping on Belgian star Axel Witsel 
Qin was shown the red card, but Witsel himself was lucky to stay on the pitch after he elbowed Fredy Guarin later on Video 24th March 2017, 1:52 pm Updated: 24th March 2017, 8:02 pm
